I am breaking up the J. Wood cabinet set I purchased at the National.  I am selling 12 of the 14 cabinets.  The ones to be sold are hall of famers (Keefe, Welch, O'Rourke, and Connor), and other NY members (Corcoran, Deasley, Dorgan, Esterbrook, Gerhardt, Gillespie, Mutrie, and Richardson).  Please e-mail me if interested.  I will sell or trade.
